erally the buffs that you have can greatly effect the outcome of a PVP combat.  I like the damage shield potions for tank classes, for example.  It's amazing what you can do when you make friends with a shaman. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub38.ezboard.com/umilassissugarfists.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Milassis Sugarfists</A> at: 10/23/01 11:56:35 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub38.ezboard.com/bmonklybusiness43508.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=shingoku>Shingoku</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 36<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/25/01 6:18:26 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=535.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: More stuff</span><hr size=1> How about monk vs. monk?  Anyone have any tactics? <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub38.ezboard.com/uzinj.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zinj</A> at: 4/2/02 8:00:39 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub38.ezboard.com/usekksi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sekksi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(1/15/02 7:33:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=535.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: More stuff</span><hr size=1> are all these things from blue servers? or actually servers like mine (ie rallos zek).<br>
