<br>
How to run:<br>
Strafing is a must, you travel slightly faster.<br>
<br>
Run on hills, use the hillbug.  The pvp system is broken. If you want to live you will have to exploit the bugs like everyone else.  <br>
<br>
Find a zone. zoning is a good getaway tatic IF you zone fast. If you don't then you could end up zoning back and forth for a while.  If I have to zone more than 3 times from a faster zoner, I usually give up and make a break for it.  Also, zoning at very low health will strip all buffs(including dots), and give you a few hp back.  Some people consider this lame, but they are usually the necros that have been hill bugging and levitating over water for 50 lvls.<br>
<br>
Fd can work on pets.  Kinda.  It might give you a half of a second lead on them, but thats long enough to find a zone.  dont stop to look behind yourself.<br>
<br>
Water: casters cant land a spell on a person in water if they are not.  Its called the water bug, its supposed to be that way so casters cant nuke things that cant leave the water.  The necro that was levitating over that cliff will call you lame.<br>
<br>
Some people might call you a chicken for running, but when your outclassed, out gunned, and on the ropes, you have two choices, run or die.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub38.ezboard.com/unilerek.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nilerek</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 28<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(1/17/02 3:40:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=535.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: running</span><hr size=1> well, in my experiences in pvp, resist gear is a MUST.  Magic resist gear is THE most important of all resists at first...  Once you get it to about 100, you can start getting the others up..<br>
<br>
<br>
Why magic first?  Simple, you do NOT want to be rooted or snared.  A rooted/snared monk is a DEAD monk.  Also, you should try to have sow/jboot on before you go PK.<br>
<br>
Against a caster:  Yes, they will try to kite you..  The trick i use is either pumice them and take off their sow, or follow them till they start to cast, then go all out on them.  They will probably keep concentration but you still do dmg to them, and casters dont have much hp.<br>
<br>
Against a melee:  Well, as an iksar monk, i have more ac than a warrior my level and more atk.  So pretty much, try to melee head on, and you will most likely win.  If the other guy tries to joust, well, dispel his sow with pumice if he has it, and if you have sow/jboot on, its a lot easier to joust when you move faster.<br>
<br>
<br>
This is pre-50 fighting btw, not high enough for post 50, but pretty much most of the same things stick.  Except for if you are fighting a caster, wait to use offensive disc till they start to gate, cause gate is the spell the will mostlike not try to move away from you when casting. <p>I play everquest!  yay!<Br>I play Tilnam and Nilerek on the Quellious server.<Br>Kazdun on Sullon Zek server also.</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showMessageRange?topicID=535.topic&start=21&stop=34>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=535.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showNextMessage?topicID=535.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=535.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.emailToFriend?topicID=535.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.threadControl?topicID=535.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=535.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=535.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td>